    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, kept tucked away in a garage and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It drives like an absolute dream and is in pristine condition inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that's basically perfect, this is the one for you. Drop me a message\u2014you're going to love it!",
      "price": 45500.0,
