    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new and ready for the road, this is the one for you! Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
