    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power unit. This specimen exhibits flawless mechanical provenance, with the high-pressure Double VANOS system recently overhauled and the rear subframe reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The 3.2L naturally aspirated straight-six delivers linear power through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. No subframe cracks, no rod bearing concerns, and zero fluid seepage. This is a turn-key, museum-quality driver for the discerning purist.",
